headline: Knowing The Pain Points Locked In Profit On GE Vernova
summary: Since swing trading relies heavily on technical analysis.  Being aware of areas of resistance as well as market strength is imperative.  For GE Vernova, our sell decisions relied on this combination to lock in a quick profit while we had it.
